{"tid":2193944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿Moon怒斥政府把關不力","createTime":"2020-09-08T08:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T09:31:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"39d582289583e32d0bcae02940792ffda87bd4c6","tid":2193944,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:16:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/ULD5D3W4GVESTLUI3RDGGXSGDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FULD5D3W4GVESTLUI3RDGGXSGDQ%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=4cbb8a38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FULD5D3W4GVESTLUI3RDGGXSGDQ%2F&h=67bc6f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/ULD5D3W4GVESTLUI3RDGGXSGDQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n阿Moon怒斥政府把關不力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5SmZYwjkJ0vee02qLwOqFYMiMVo=/2213x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TT6PGEXPOZFRREKNGVE723ZJKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5SmZYwjkJ0vee02qLwOqFYMiMVo%3D%2F2213x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTT6PGEXPOZFRREKNGVE723ZJKE.jpg&h=9c21e050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■回想到只能隔着玻璃送別雙親，阿Moon傷痛不已。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多個醫學研究證實，引爆第三波疫情的病毒是由豁免檢疫的海員及機師帶入香港；政府中門大開的免檢疫漏洞，導致很多像阿Moon父母一樣的無辜者染疫死亡。阿Moon直斥政府把關疏忽，「之前睇新聞見到老人院嘅老人家，無出街都感染同死亡，都好心悒；輪到自己爸爸媽媽唔知喺邊度感染，最終走埋，係好無辜好唔抵」。短時間內雙親離世，阿Moon心如刀割，外間有不少聲音要求政府向死者家屬道歉、賠償，但對阿Moon沒有意義，「賠幾多畀我，都賠唔番爸爸媽媽畀我！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「賠幾多都賠唔番爸媽畀我」<br />\n<br />\n首兩波疫情持續約半年，香港僅八宗死亡；但第三波疫情不足三個月，已逾90人離世。阿Moon斥政府把關不力，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。外界不少聲音要求政府為疫情失控及造成近百人死亡負責、道歉，甚至賠償；但對阿Moon來說，父母不能回到她身邊，才最令她感到遺憾，「就算道歉，爸爸媽媽都係一樣救唔番；賠償只當係小小慰問心意，但賠幾多畀我，都賠唔番爸爸媽媽畀我！」<br />\n<br />\n阿Moon希望不再有其他人像她一樣因疫情失去至親，也不希望香港再有第四、五波疫情，盼政府能完善政策，保障市民健康。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"fa22afc06d40148483c4b9274fb5c4dc79e7ed09","tid":2193944,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> RIP"},{"pid":"1516d608dcd42369030ad8b56edb4730e01d503b","tid":2193944,"uid":333199,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"以為係劉佩玥"},{"pid":"6056e01ee40ac463725807dbe67c82dfedb2bb26","tid":2193944,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"應該聯同美國一齊索償<br />\n一條命一億<br />\n充供中共美債及貪官境外黑錢去賠償<br />\n香港人有事無事就推呢個做文宣"},{"pid":"e0146ba4b58883d0e6347b608c0879d287c70778","tid":2193944,"uid":231103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持住"},{"pid":"23ca3dfde3430fa60babe02ec665e750647bca05","tid":2193944,"uid":54415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"呢個港共想再孭百幾條人命, 03有299都冇再理..."},{"pid":"22cdb327f16fa60ba4a4706bde7f569bb33d08d0","tid":2193944,"uid":114074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"咁短時間突然雙親走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難接受到<br />\n其實點解呢一波死咁多人"},{"pid":"83cda9a149b5ded3be6b47df7fe6fac2146d4dbf","tid":2193944,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951f0fa78bf7938a6572dac5a3f6d0998d22fa18","tid":2193944,"uid":20317,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T08:42:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8fb067158b8eeceac4c017cf